Changes to Diff
===============

07-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Bugfix: selection of unified mode from options was broken, reported by
        Peter Hyman.

11-Sep-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Remove aclocal.m4, replace with rox-clib.m4 and aclocal -I .

27-May-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Detect getopt_long.

23-Nov-2004 (2.1.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added missing libdir script.

31 Oct 2004 (2.1.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Update to new interfaces for infowin and choices.

2.1.0
-----
Use ROX-CLib 2.1.0, including aclocal.m4.
Stock icons in the menu.

2.0.0
-----
Stable release to go with ROX-CLib 2.0.0.

1.1.3
-----
Italian translation of AppInfo provided by Yuri Bongiorno.
Safer way to parse ROX-CLib's version number by Christopher Arndt.

1.1.2
-----
New icon provided by Geoff Youngs.  Use new options system.  Setting font
for text windows works.

1.1.1
-----
Gtk+ 2.0.

1.1.0
-----
Can process unified diffs as well as context diffs.
Fix for compiling when pathname contains spaces.

1.0.3
-----
Fix compilation problems with libxml2.

1.0.2
-----
Fix for getting incomplete lines because of buffering.

1.0.1
-----
Make sure AppRun can find rox_run.

1.0.0
-----
Added support for shared ROX-CLib.

0.1.2
-----
Added -h and -v options.

0.1.1
-----
Added an icon.  Check for <sys/filio.h>.

0.1.0
-----
First version.
